key_trends: Adoption of hybrid storage solutions (RAM + Flash)

competitive_positioning.differentiation: Speed and cost-effectiveness due to in-memory caching and FLASH persistence combination.
competitive_advantages: More cost-effective than pure in-memory solutions
competitive_vulnerabilities: Potential complexity in managing hybrid storage

growth_indicators: Expansion into new use cases (e.g., real-time analytics)

key_risks: Emergence of competing hybrid database solutions
Difficulty in maintaining performance at scale

next_steps: Focus on specific use cases (e.g., gaming, ad tech)
Develop strong partnerships with cloud providers
